                     <interp inst="t18510915-1820-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>, stealing 1 bridle, 1 wanty, and other harness, value 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18510915-name-258" type="victimName">
